This paper describes a strategy for using social media data to identify individuals at risk for preventable chronic illness, specifically type 2 diabetes mellitus. The approach involves using a game-like quiz to collect relevant data from individuals on a voluntary basis. This paper could fit into several arXiv CS sub-categories, but the most likely are cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). The paper also involves machine learning and data analysis, which could place it in sub-categories such as cs.SD (Software Development) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing and text analysis, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language).
